title: Changes in the Big Ten
description:
Jason Fitz, Tom Luginbill, and Harry Lyles Jr. react to the reports of Texas and Oklahoma leaving the Big 12 for the SEC. Also, Big Ten Media Days continue, and the crew discuss season expectations for Ohio State.
